          "value": "禁止向上述美国实体出口两用物项；正在开展的相关出口活动应当立即停止",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Prohibit the export of dual-use items to the above US entity; ongoing related export activities should be immediately ceased",
